oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jack Greene and Jeannie Seely at the Veterans Memorial Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Greene, Jack (Singer); Seely, Jeannie;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing Jack Greene and Jeannie Seely show with Don Frost at the Columbus Veterans Auditorium on June 1. Poster features metal photoplates of Jack Greene, Jeannie Seely, Don Frost, and the Home Grown Blue Grass Boys.
